Class HttpConsumer.Factory

  • java.lang.Object
    • se.arkalix.net.http.consumer.HttpConsumer.Factory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ArConsumerFactory<HttpConsumer>
    Enclosing interface:
    HttpConsumer
    public static class HttpConsumer.Factory
extends java.lang.Object
implements ArConsumerFactory<HttpConsumer>
    Class used for creating HttpConsumer instances.

    This class is primarily useful as input to the using() method of the ServiceQuery class, an instance of which is returned by the ArSystem.consume() method. See the package documentation for more details about how this class can be used.

    Use the HttpConsumer.factory() method to get an instance of this class.
